title: Handel - The Masterworks (40 CDs)
description:
Music : Classical : Lossless



This is a compilation of various works from G.F. Handel (1685-1759) presented in a 40CD Box Set by Briliant Classics. Inside, you will find: 

Jephtha
Belsazar
Messiah
Brockes Passion
Johannes Passion
Acis & Galatea
Imeneo
Faramondo
Rinaldo
Coronation Anthems
Italian Cantantas
Deutsche Arien
Water Music
Music for the Royal Fireworks
Concerto grossi Op.3 & 6 (complete)
Organ Concertos (complete)
Chamber Music (complete)

Scans have been provided. CD's were ripped to FLAC level 6 and CUE sheets have been provided as well. 

Enjoy.
